    "title": "Now Hiring Store Manager at Reliance Digital",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Store Manager with drive and ambition, Reliance Digital in Vijayawada is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Reliance Digital:\nReliance Digital is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Reliance Digital!",
